Loading packages and setting

library(tidyverse) # data manipulation
library(lubridate) # time data handling
library(ggplot2) # visualization
library(ggridges) # ridges plot
options(stringsAsFactors = FALSE)
basic_theme <- function() {
  theme_minimal() +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, size = 15),
        plot.subtitle = element_text(hjust = 0.5, size = 12),
        plot.margin = unit(c(5, 10, 5, 10), "mm"),
        axis.title.x = element_text(vjust = -1),
        axis.title.y = element_text(vjust = 3),
        text = element_text(family = "PingFangTC-Regular"))
}

Loading raw data and preprocessing

per16 <- read.csv("dataset/2016/A05_basic_all.csv", header = TRUE, sep = ",")
don16 <- read.csv("dataset/2016/A02_company_all_public.csv", header = TRUE, sep = ",")
per12 <- read.csv("dataset/2012/A15_basicall_8.csv", header = TRUE, sep = ",")
don12 <- read.csv("dataset/2012/political_donation_8_od.csv", header = TRUE, sep = ",")
per08 <- read.csv("dataset/2008/A16_basicall_7.csv", header = TRUE, sep = ",")
don08 <- read.csv("dataset/2008/political_donation_7_od.csv", header = TRUE, sep = ",")

don16 <- don16 %>%
  select(-, -, -, -, -, -, -P) %>%
  rename( = ) %>%
  mutate( = as.character(),  = "9")
don12 <- don12 %>%
  select(-, -, -) %>%
  rename( = .) %>%
  mutate( = as.character(),  = as.character())
don08 <- don08 %>%
  select(-, -) %>%
  rename( = .) %>%
  mutate( = as.character())

donation <- bind_rows(bind_rows(don08, don12), don16)
donation <- donation %>%
  rename( = .,  = ) %>%
  mutate( = as.Date(.$, format = "%Y/%m/%d") %m+% years(1911))

per08 <- cbind(per08,  = "7")
per12 <- cbind(per12,  = "8")
per16 <- per16 %>% mutate( = "9") %>%
  select(-3, -9, -12, -15, -17, -19, -21, -23, -25, -26, -27) %>% 
  mutate_at(vars(11:16), funs(as.integer(gsub("," , "", .))))

person <- bind_rows(bind_rows(per08, per12), per16)
person <- mutate(person,  = as.integer(gsub("%", "", person$)) / 100)

Data preprocessing

business_cat_political <- donation %>%
  distinct(, , ) %>%
  left_join(person, by = c("", "")) %>%
  filter( %in% c("", "")) %>%
  group_by(, ) %>%
  count() %>%
  filter(n > 1) %>% 
  mutate( = ifelse(n >= 1 & n <= 2, "",
                    ifelse(n >= 3 & n <= 5, "", ""))) %>%
  rename( = n)

donation_political <- donation %>%
  distinct(, , ) %>%
  left_join(person, by = c("", "")) %>%
  filter( %in% c("", "")) %>%
  group_by(, , ) %>%
  count() %>% 
  ungroup() %>%
  inner_join(business_cat_political, by = c("", "")) %>%
  mutate( = ifelse( == "", n, 0),
          = factor(, levels = c("7", "8", "9")))

donation_political_low <- donation_political %>%
  filter( == "") %>%
  group_by(, , ) %>%
  summarise( = sum()) %>%
  mutate( =  / )

ggplot(donation_political_low, aes(x = , y = , fill = )) +
  geom_density_ridges(alpha = 0.9) +
  labs(x = "", y = "",
       title = "") +
  scale_fill_discrete(name = "") +
  scale_y_discrete(limits = rev(levels(donation_political_low$))) +
  basic_theme()

donation_political_medium <- donation_political %>%
  filter( == "") %>%
  group_by(, , ) %>%
  summarise( = sum()) %>%
  mutate( =  / )

ggplot(donation_political_medium, aes(x = , y = , fill = )) +

donation_political_high <- donation_political %>%

Data preprocessing

business_cat_winning <- donation %>%
  distinct(, , ) %>%
  left_join(person, by = c("", "")) %>%
  filter( %in% c("", "")) %>%
  group_by(, ) %>%
  count() %>%
  mutate( = ifelse(n >= 1 & n <= 2, "",
                    ifelse(n >= 3 & n <= 5, "", ""))) %>%
  rename( = n)

donation_winning <- donation %>%
  distinct(, , ) %>%
  inner_join(person, by = c("", "")) %>%
  group_by(, ) %>%
  count(, ) %>%
  inner_join(business_cat_winning, by = c("", "")) %>%
  mutate(value = ifelse( == "*", n, 0),
          = factor(, levels = c("7", "8", "9")))

donation_winning_low <- donation_winning %>%
  filter( == "") %>%
  group_by(, ) %>%
  summarise( = sum(value) / sum(n))

ggplot(donation_winning_low, aes(x = , y = , fill = )) +
  geom_density_ridges(alpha = 0.9) +
  labs(x = "", y = "",
       title = "") +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = c(0, 0.5, 1)) +
  scale_fill_discrete(name = "") +
  scale_y_discrete(limits = rev(levels(donation_political_high$))) +
  basic_theme()

Iron donation of KMT and DPP

Data preprocessing

donate_three <- donation %>%
  distinct(, ) %>%
  group_by() %>%
  count() %>%
  filter(n == 3)

donate_three_kuo <- donation %>%
  filter( %in% donate_three$) %>%
  inner_join(person %>% select(, , ), by = c("", "")) %>%
  mutate(value = case_when( == "" ~ 0, TRUE ~ 1)) %>%
  group_by(, ) %>%
  summarise(all_value = sum(value)) %>%
  group_by() %>%
  summarise(kuo = sum(all_value)) %>%
  filter(kuo == 0)

donate_three_min <- donation %>%
  filter( %in% donate_three$) %>%
  inner_join(person %>% select(, , ), by = c("", "")) %>%
  mutate(value = case_when( == "" ~ 0, TRUE ~ 1)) %>%
  group_by(, ) %>%
  summarise(all_value = sum(value)) %>%
  group_by() %>%
  summarise(min = sum(all_value)) %>%
  filter(min == 0)

An overview of iron donation

donate_three_kuomin <- donation %>%
  filter( %in% c(donate_three_kuo$, donate_three_min$)) %>%
  mutate( = case_when( %in% donate_three_kuo$ ~ "",
                           TRUE ~ "")) %>%
  group_by(, ) %>%
  summarise(all = sum())

ggplot(donate_three_kuomin) +
